div.div:
Researchers at Janelia perform experiments, storing recording outputs
following predefined directory structure and file-naming convention:
Behavioral data - animal, session, trials, photo-stimulation, etc.
Tracking data - raw video tracking from multiple camera, tracked features output from DLC
Electrophysiology - output files of neuropixels recording (SpikeGLX)
Histology - CCF coordinates of the inserted probes and electrodes
Researchers perform spike clustering analysis, quality control and post-processing
